dct_title_s: Exquisita & magno aliquot mensium periculo lustrata et iam retecta Freti Magellanici Facies = Eijgentlicke afbeeldinghe der Magellanischer Strate : die nu met veel gevaers ettelijeke Maenden doorsien, van nieus ondeckt is
dct_description_sm: Publication information in Spanish. Relief shown pictorially. Depths shown by soundings. Oriented with north to bottom. "Descripción del mapa: Estrecho de Magallanes. Original impreso en 1630." Includes inset of "Dese eijlanden die in gheene Pascaerten aengeteeckent bevonden en worden, ...."
